metadata.name: Would you like fries with that?
metadata.description:
An 10 hour Open Edition with 1 burn event happening in January to redeem "I'm Rekt".

Created after a particularly rough day and all I could think about was how am I going to survive. As an artist I feel like I straddle the line between greatness and a job working at McDonalds. Would my art provide utility as a container for fast food takeout?
